episodes.title: Woman, who went missing from Isha centre in Coimbatore, found dead | The Federal
episodes.description:
#ishayogacenter | #Coimbatore 

The body of a 34-year-old woman, who went missing on December 18, has been recovered from a well in Coimbatore. Police identified the victim as Subashree, a resident of Avinashi in Tiruppur district, who went missing after attending an eight-day yoga programme at Isha Yoga Centre in Coimbatore.
